---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import aboutImage from '../../assets/images/about-me-image.jpg';
import '../../assets/styles/AboutMe.css';
---

<div class="about-section" id="aboutme">
  <h2>ABOUT ME</h2>
  <div class="row align-items-center">
    <div class="about-image">
      <Image src={aboutImage} alt="Casey Hsu" />
    </div>
    <div class="about-text">
      <p>I'm a full-stack web developer based in Toronto, building production websites for
        e-commerce, agency, and retail clients. My current projects span
        <strong>WordPress</strong>, <strong>HubSpot CMS</strong>, and <strong>Shopify</strong> —
        from custom theme builds and platform migrations to performance optimization and
        API integrations.
      </p>
      <p>Before moving into development, I spent nine years leading culinary teams — managing
        high-pressure operations, coaching staff, and optimizing workflows. That experience
        gave me a strong foundation in deadline management, client communication, and
        cross-functional collaboration that I bring to every project.
      </p>
      <p>I graduated from George Brown College's Computer Programming and Analysis program
        with Dean's List honors, and I'm a <strong>Contentful Certified Professional</strong>
        with expertise in headless CMS architecture and personalization. I work with
        JavaScript, React, Node.js, Docker, and modern CI/CD tooling.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
